        Introduction to the SplProgram

    doc:    https://solana.com/docs/tokens
            https://solana.com/docs/tokens/basics
    github:
        SplToken source: git@github.com:solana-program/token.git
        AssociatedSplTokenAccount: git@github.com:solana-program/associated-token-account.git


    1. To understand functionality of the spl-token contract try to use spl-token utility:
        - run solana-validator

        - create a new token:
            $ spl-token create-token
            Creating token 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14 under program TokenkegQfeZyiNwAJbNbGKPFXCWuBvf9Ss623VQ5DA

            Address:  8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14
            Decimals:  9


        - create spl-account associated with your Solana wallet:
            $ spl-token create-account 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14
            Creating account EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44

            Signature: 5UABCnm1WnzJeNxMyjuUrEfiUJFMosQuKHnmtoHpFQPT9ZX96zmFSDjffSa25F3XExgXqUd19irhsFzWS3PyJVvp

        - mint funds to your spl-account:
        $ spl-token mint 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14 100
        Minting 100 tokens
          Token: 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14
          Recipient: EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44

        Signature: 3eDxGZ34ozcHiAiBdPVuHyqsScgPTPjdwYkq8jz8qweDw1kwnmvaxyyRAuE5QCsQpq8sUfh3PV1kGjNLHjjfcUGw


        - take a look at result:
        $ spl-token accounts -v
        Program                                       Token                                         Account                                       Delegated  Close Authority  Balance
        -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        TokenkegQfeZyiNwAJbNbGKPFXCWuBvf9Ss623VQ5DA   8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14  EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44                              100


        - create a new Solana account:
        $   solana-keygen new --no-bip39-passphrase -s -o new.json

        - display the pubkey of the new account:
        $ solana address -k new.json
        FwSJMHY8VAnourNMiGDu2vtQG3q9oV7E8WQxXvj7wizD

        - airdrop funds:
        $ solana airdrop 1 new.json
        Requesting airdrop of 1 SOL

        Signature: 2UyNJ2dFP9hrSMKwNnoomKA2ywvhfUuMbExbUdCY1vV9w2ir2Hpia5WDa5yQ4UJqLte49bb48CXYuzNPuTtiaMct

        1 SOL

        - create spl-account associated with the new.json account:
        $ spl-token create-account 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14 --owner FwSJMHY8VAnourNMiGDu2vtQG3q9oV7E8WQxXvj7wizD --fee-payer new.json
        Creating account 6u7kTfzC8gzyA6kzbbG3kQMdycJPigaYcqqht1tBjryR

        Signature: 3t3R6HkaZysLpYTXBh936H7AftdmFx2Lbq3g844EG7iFZKx7WHNjeNVBTSwgt6qLNcLuZc214HZhbmQiZ5bqS3Rm

        - transfer spl-tokens to spl-account associated with new.json
        $ spl-token transfer 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14 1 6u7kTfzC8gzyA6kzbbG3kQMdycJPigaYcqqht1tBjryR
         Transfer 1 tokens
           Sender: EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44
           Recipient: 6u7kTfzC8gzyA6kzbbG3kQMdycJPigaYcqqht1tBjryR

         Signature: 642UKGq9jL1DY8RZRjeaQXX8XKxTXF6d5ggjvxGXWrVyTUBC8JNooQJ5wNqMSE2zAV7WwtbmTfXgyEZSgwishz9u

        - result:
        $ spl-token balance --address 6u7kTfzC8gzyA6kzbbG3kQMdycJPigaYcqqht1tBjryR
        1

        - approve 5 tokens to the new.json account:
        $  spl-token approve EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44 5 FwSJMHY8VAnourNMiGDu2vtQG3q9oV7E8WQxXvj7wizD
        Approve 5 tokens
          Account: EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44
          Delegate: FwSJMHY8VAnourNMiGDu2vtQG3q9oV7E8WQxXvj7wizD

        Signature: 4CigsocP1ttKGB5JBjzzj5oBWM2mXedLL1jMusHqY51pY6huMyT1czqNLfenG8UKciLPf4MuJwsZ4qqq2EAiLcPv

        - check the result:
        $ spl-token display EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44

        SPL Token Account
          Address: EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44
          Program: TokenkegQfeZyiNwAJbNbGKPFXCWuBvf9Ss623VQ5DA
          Balance: 79
          Decimals: 9
          Mint: 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14
          Owner: AwsrRzgubeCsP77GNRdGCH4XefWkczFPrAzm86q7gVv4
          State: Initialized
          Delegation:
            Delegate: FwSJMHY8VAnourNMiGDu2vtQG3q9oV7E8WQxXvj7wizD
            Allowance: 5
          Close authority: (not set)


        - create another one Solana wallet:
        $ solana-keygen new --no-bip39-passphrase -s -o other.json
        Wrote new keypair to other.json

        - get pubkey of the other.json Solana-account:
        $ solana address -k other.json
            81XNRa9hbsMcytdtZCi13qbBCjvmNPJKidTLSuNMxfsS

        - transfer 5 tokens from EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44 to other.json using new.json keypair to sign transaction:
        $ spl-token transfer --owner new.json    --from EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44 --allow-unfunded-recipient --fund-recipient 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14 5 81XNRa9hbsMcytdtZCi13qbBCjvmNPJKidTLSuNMxfsS
        Transfer 5 tokens
          Sender: EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44
          Recipient: 81XNRa9hbsMcytdtZCi13qbBCjvmNPJKidTLSuNMxfsS
          Recipient associated token account: 7dRQuTJkGW8KN2Wzt2cAXdThXUdxePFnobdxtu4Cvbx5

        Signature: 2kSSka6M21mpsamv6XeepUK8Ux9jdykGRWxQbMe6h8P6useenwmWVi2CweH3tdES7kwyTDwnLkDVGD5hZgQhPe4Q

        This transfer can be called transfer_from operation. The account new.json transferred tokens from the spl-acccount
        that is not associated with it.  The approved tokens are used.

        -make sure that all appoved tokens are spent:
        $ spl-token display EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44

        SPL Token Account
          Address: EjS8MtoofhoF1VCJhSyhkvKAFJAUGuKvAaUmirQj9X44
          Program: TokenkegQfeZyiNwAJbNbGKPFXCWuBvf9Ss623VQ5DA
          Balance: 74
          Decimals: 9
          Mint: 8QvKCrvUWjR8emErThAM9xkF4RxMNSF1mPXqofURhA14
          Owner: AwsrRzgubeCsP77GNRdGCH4XefWkczFPrAzm86q7gVv4
          State: Initialized
          Delegation: (not set)
          Close authority: (not set)


    2. add Deposit instruction to your hello-world contract.
    instruction processing:
        - create a contract wallet:
            create pda-account derived from program_id. This should be done only once.
        - create a spl-account associated with the contract wallet.
        - transfer spl-token from the spl-account associated with signer to the spl-account associated with contract wallet
        - create user-account inside state of the contract:
            create a pda-account derived from signer's pubkey.
        - mint funds of user-account: write number of transferred tokens to user-account. Let's call it wrapped-spl-tokens.

    steps to reproduce:
        - create spl-token
        - create spl-account associated with signer account
        - mint spl-token to the spl-account associated with signer account
        - create the transaction to deposit funds to the contract
        - Create other signer account, mint funds to it. Call the deposit using the new sigher.
        - Check spl-balance of the contract wallet.

    3. impl internal transfer instruction
        - transfer wrapped-spl tokens from user1-account to user2-account. This transfer affects only pda-accounts of the contract.

    4. impl withdraw instruction
         - transfer spl-tokens from the contract wallet to spl-account associated with signer.
         - burn wrapped-spl-tokens of the user-account.

    5. Optionally.
    create the spl-account associated with the payer account and use it as user-account inside the state of the contract.
    Impl Deposit, internal transfer and withdraw instructions using this type of user-account.




